headline: The Dividend Aristocrat With 53% Margins Just Widened the Gap on the Frozen Dividend Competitor
summary: Kraft Heinz (NASDAQ: KHC) and PepsiCo (NASDAQ: PEP) both beat Q3 2025 earnings, but the results highlight two packaged food giants on starkly different trajectories.
